data.description: Beautiful custom home in desirable Sehoy subdivision with plenty of space for everyone! This stunning property features 5 full bedrooms (one could be used as a bonus/theater room), 3 full bathrooms, split floor-plan, and a large cul-de-sac lot! Home has been updated with beautiful engineered hard wood floors throughout main level living areas and primary bedroom, solid surface counter tops in kitchen as well as tile backsplash and fresh paint upstairs. Farmhouse touches in the primary suite such as a barn door, shiplap, and beautiful custom tile around soaking tub, add to the huge primary closet to make this a retreat! Two more guest rooms, a full bath, dining room and breakfast room round out the lower level while upstairs you have two more rooms as well as a full bath and plenty of storage! There is even a storage room under the home that could be used as a storm shelter. Outside features sprinkler system, hard-wired security cameras, roof was replaced in 2020, and upstairs AC was replaced in 2020. This beautiful home won't last long....come see it today!
